---
import Snowfall from '../components/Snowfall.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Put your back pain on ice.</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/landing.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>❄️</text></svg>">
  </head>
  <body>
    <Snowfall />
    <div id="snow"></div>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <header>
        <h1>Put your back pain on ice.</h1>
        <p>The world's first cold therapy foam roller, designed to freeze inflammation and restore mobility.</p>
        <a class="cta-button" href="https://www.kickstarter.com" target="_blank">
          Back us on Kickstarter
          <span class="cta-snowflake">🧊 🧊 🧊 </span>
        </a>
      </header>

      <section>
        <h2>The Problem</h2>
        <p>Traditional foam rollers warm up after minutes. Ice packs slide off. You need pressure <strong>and</strong> cold and you need it to last.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Meet Backblizzard</h2>
        <p>A purpose-built foam roller with a freezable cold core and a firm-yet-comfortable surface.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>🧊 Holds cold for 25+ minutes</li>
            <li>🧘 Extra-wide design for full back coverage</li>
            <li>🛞 Durable, non-slip exterior</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="circle-img-row">
          <div class="circle-img">
            <img src="/one.png" alt="Backblizzard Roller 1" />
          </div>
          <div class="circle-img">
            <img src="/two.png" alt="Backblizzard Roller 2" />
          </div>
          <div class="circle-img">
            <img src="/three.png" alt="Backblizzard Roller 3" />
          </div>
          <div class="circle-img">
            <img src="/four.png" alt="Backblizzard Roller 3" />
          </div>
          <div class="hover-hide-img" id="convert">
            <img src="/two.png" alt="Backblizzard Roller 2" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="convert-caption">Hover to see roller expand to fit icepack</span>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Why It Works</h2>
        <table>
          <tr><th>Feature</th><th>Why It Matters</th></tr>
          <tr><td>🧊 Freezable core</td><td>Targets inflammation deeply</td></tr>
          <tr><td>🐚 High-density shell</td><td>Supports deep muscle release</td></tr>
          <tr><td>🧘 Ergonomic design</td><td>Aligns with your spine</td></tr>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Early Backer Rewards</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>🚀 Exclusive early-bird pricing (never offered again)</li>
  <li>🎁 Access to premium recovery routines & content library</li>
  <li>🛠️ Direct influence on product features & design choices</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>My Story</h2>
        <div class="my-story-flex">
          <div>
            <p>
              Hi, I'm Dean, creator of <i>Backblizzard</i>. After years of struggling with back pain and trying every foam roller and ice pack on the market, I realized nothing truly combined deep cold therapy with the pressure and support I needed. So I set out to design a better solution. One that could help people like me recover faster and move better every day. Thank you for supporting this journey!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="my-story-img">
                <img src="/face.jpg" alt="Creator portrait" style="border-radius: 50%; width: 160px; height: 160px; object-fit: cover; display: block; margin: 0 auto;" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Freeze your pain, not your progress.</h2>
        <a class="cta-button" href="https://www.kickstarter.com" target="_blank">
          Back us on Kickstarter
          <span class="cta-snowflake">❄️ ❄️ ❄️ ❄️</span>
        </a>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <p>Made with ❄️ by Backblizzard</p>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
      // Snowflake burst effect on CTA hover
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        document.querySelectorAll('.cta-button').forEach(btn => {
          btn.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
            btn.classList.add('snowburst');
            setTimeout(() => btn.classList.remove('snowburst'), 800);
          });
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>